fields.title: Realme X
fields.description: Realme X (Global Version) comes with 6.53 inches high-quality AMOLED screen. Both front and back sides are protected by strong 5th generation Gorilla Glasses. It has a Max-View with pop-up front camera design. The back camera is of dual 48+5 MP with PDAF, LED flash, depth sensor etc. and 4K Ultra HD video recording with gyro-EIS for Full HD recording. The front camera is of 16 MP. Realme X Global Version comes with 3765 mAh battery with 20W VOOC fast charging. It has 4, 6 or 8 GB RAM, up to 2.2 GHz octa-core CPU and Adreno 616 GPU. It is powered by Qualcomm Snapdragon 710 (10 nm) chipset. The device comes with 64, 128, 256 GB internal storage and no MicroSD slot. There is an in-display fingerprint sensor in this phone.

fields.title: Vivo V27e
fields.description: Vivo V27e comes with 6.62 inches Full HD+ AMOLED screen. It has a punch-hole front camera design. The back camera is of triple 64+2+2 MP with PDAF, OIS, depth sensor, macro lens, Ring-LED flash etc. and 4K video recording. The front camera is of 32 MP. Vivo V27e comes with 4600 mAh battery with 66W Fast Charging. It has 8 GB RAM, up to 2.2 GHz octa-core CPU and Mali-G57 MC2 GPU. It is powered by a MediaTek Helio G99 (6 nm) chipset. The device comes with 128 GB internal storage and shared MicroSD slot. There is an in-display (optical) fingerprint sensor in this phone.

fields.title: Oppo F21 Pro 5G
fields.description: Oppo F21 Pro 5G comes with 6.43 inches Full HD+ AMOLED screen. It has a left punch-hole front camera design. The back camera is of triple 64+2+2 MP with PDAF, LED flash, f/1.7 aperture, macro lens, depth sensor, etc. features and Full HD video recording option. The front camera is of 16 MP. Oppo F21 Pro 5G comes with 4500 mAh battery with 33W fast charging.

fields.title: Samsung Galaxy A14
fields.description: Samsung Galaxy A14 comes with 6.6 inches Full HD+ PLS LCD screen. It has a waterdrop notch front camera design. The back camera is of triple 50+5+2 MP with PDAF, f/1.8 aperture, ultrawide, dedicated macro camera etc. and Full HD video recording. The front camera is of 8 MP. Galaxy A14 comes with 5000 mAh battery with 15W fast charging.

fields.title: Apple iPhone 14 Plus
fields.description: Apple iPhone 14 Plus comes with a 6.7 inches Super Retina XDR OLED Full HD+ screen. It has a classical Apple iPhone notch design. The back camera is of dual 12+12 MP with powerful image processing capability and 4K video recording. The front one is of Dual 12 MP and SL 3D camera. Apple iPhone 14 Plus comes with  mAh battery with  fast charging solution. It has 4 GB RAM, up to 3.23 GHz Hexa-core CPU and Apple GPU.

fields.title: OnePlus Nord CE 3 Lite 5G
fields.description: OnePlus Nord CE 3 Lite 5G comes with 6.72 inches Full HD+ IPS LCD screen. It has a center punch-hole front camera design. The back camera is of triple 108+2+2 MP with PDAF, f/1.8 aperture, macro, depth sensor, LED flash etc. and Full HD video recording. The front camera is of 16 Megapixel. OnePlus Nord CE 3 Lite 5G comes with 5000 mAh battery with 67W fast charging. It has 8 GB RAM, up to 2.2 GHz octa-core CPU and Adreno 619 GPU.

fields.title: OnePlus Nord 2 5G
fields.description: OnePlus Nord 2 5G comes with 6.43 inches Full HD+ Fluid AMOLED screen. It has a left punch-hole front camera design. The back camera is of triple 50+8+2 MP with PDAF, OIS, ultrawide, monochrome, dual-LED flash etc. and Ultra HD video recording. The front camera is of 32 Megapixel. OnePlus Nord 2 5G comes with 4500 mAh battery with 65W fast charging. It has 8 or 12 GB RAM.

fields.title: Nokia G20
fields.description: Nokia G20 comes with 6.52 inches HD+ IPS LCD screen. It has a punch-hole front camera design. The back camera is of Quad 48+5+2+2 Megapixel with PDAF, LED flash, depth sensor, macro, ultrawide etc. and Full HD video recording. The front camera is of 8 MP. Nokia G20 comes with 5050 mAh battery and 10W fast charging. It has 4 GB RAM, up to 2.3GHz octa-core CPU and PowerVR GE8320 GPU.

fields.title: Symphony ATOM 3
fields.description: Symphony ATOM 3 comes with 6.6 inches HD+ IPS screen. It has a Full-View waterdrop-notch design. The back camera is of Dual 8 MP main camera with autofocus, LED Flash, portrait mode, night mode etc. and HD video recording. The front camera is of 5 MP. Symphony ATOM 3 comes with 5070 mAh big battery. It has 3 GB RAM, 2.0 GHz octa-core CPU and PowerVR GE8300 GPU.
